---
/**
 * FAQSection Component
 * 
 * Displays frequently asked questions about the AppMRR leaderboard.
 * Includes information about:
 * - API key security
 * - Data update frequency
 * - Revenue calculation limitations
 * - How to delete an app
 * 
 * Uses HTML details/summary for collapsible Q&A items
 * 
 * Used in: index.astro
 */
---

<section class="faq-section">
	<div class="card faq-card">
		<div class="faq-header">
			<h2>FAQ</h2>
			<p class="faq-subtitle">Common questions about data and privacy</p>
		</div>
		<div class="faq-list">
			<details>
				<summary>Are my keys safe?</summary>
				<p>
					We only require a RevenueCat API key with <strong>read-only</strong> access to "Chart metrics". Keys are stored encrypted at rest and never shared publicly. You can revoke the key from RevenueCat at any time.
				</p>
			</details>

			<details>
				<summary>How frequent are data updating?</summary>
				<p>
					Metrics are refreshed automatically on a daily basis (midnight UTC). We aim to keep the leaderboard current without requiring manual updates.
				</p>
			</details>

			<details>
				<summary>Why can't I see full time revenue?</summary>
				<p>
					RevenueCat's API only returns revenue for the last 28 days. We are working on a solution to display all-time revenue with graphs and charts.
				</p>
			</details>

			<details>
				<summary>How can I delete my app?</summary>
				<p>
					You can delete your app revoking the API key from RevenueCat. It will be removed from the leaderboard within 24 hours (when the next daily update runs).
				</p>
			</details>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.faq-section {
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.card {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
		border-radius: 8px;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.faq-card {
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}

	.faq-header h2 {
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: var(--fg);
	}

	.faq-subtitle {
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.faq-list details {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding: 0.75rem 0;
	}

	.faq-list details:first-of-type {
		border-top: none;
	}

	.faq-list summary {
		cursor: pointer;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--fg);
		list-style: none;
	}

	.faq-list summary::-webkit-details-marker {
		display: none;
	}

	.faq-list p {
		margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
</style>

